January 8, 1996

Contracts: Cyber Digital, Inc.

          Cyber Digital, Inc., has signed a memorandum of
understanding calling for National Telecommunications Co. of
Egypt and its parent, The National Bank of Egypt, to fund a $20
million contract between the Republic of Tajikistan and Cyber for
telecom systems.  National Telecom and Cyber also will form a
joint venture to create and operate a telephone company in
Tajikistan.



