January 8, 1996

M & A: MobileMedia Corp.

          MobileMedia Corp. has completed its $930 million acquisition
of MobileComm, the paging unit of BellSouth Corp. (TR, Sept. 18,
1995), making it the second-largest paging company in the U.S.,
behind Paging Network, Inc.  MobileMedia will serve more than 4
million subscribers and collect more than $560 million in annual
revenues as a result...



<A HREF ="#HeadList">Back to Headline List</A><BR>
