Industry News: Sprint Communications Co. L.P

          Sprint Communications Co. L.P. is offering small businesses
free calling on Fridays for one year through its new "Fridays
Free" promotion.  New customers signing up for a Sprint calling
plan with at least $50 in monthly charges will be eligible.  The
plan provides free domestic and international interexchange
calling, cellular long distance service, fax service, calling
card calling, and incoming toll-free calling, Sprint said.  The
maximum free usage is capped at $1,000 per month...



