screen to show how eyes perform under VDU operation
as well for normal sight... SSP INTERNATIONAL in the
UK has launched an Internet service providing betting
on Japanese sporting events such as sumo and soccer:
as the site is not based in Japan it is not subject
to the country's strict betting regulations... Author
