will take the form of a graphic multimedia novel,
made available through the Internet...  Most BRITISH
professional workers fear, according to a TSB survey,
that their skills have been outdated by new
technology, meaning that they are no longer
guaranteed a career for life and that technology has
brought longer working hours and new demands from
employers... BELL CABLEMEDIA in the UK has reported a
