CEO: Ir Bob Benneker
Area Of Operation: Consultancy and Training
in Telecom and Post
Alliances: Svana Systems (P) Ltd
No. Of Employees: 60
Address In India: Svana Systems (P) Ltd,
D28, Panchsheel Enclave, New Delhi - 110 017
Tel.: 011-6220560/6868906
Fax: 011-6433931/6511231

DHIRAJ AHUJA

