a quarterly management fee at the annual percentage rate of the
relevant Fund's average daily net assets set forth below. The
Manager has agreed to voluntarily waive some or all of its management
fee and, if necessary, to bear certain expenses of each Fund until
further notice to the extent required to limit the total annual
operating expenses (which do not include nonrecurring account
fees and extraordinary expenses) of each class of shares to the
percentage of each Fund's average daily net assets attributable
to that class listed in the Expense Limitation column below. 
