the amount invested in the particular Fund and whether the investor
makes the investment directly or through a financial adviser.
The three classes of shares are Institutional Shares, Adviser
Shares and Select Shares. Each class of shares is generally subject
to a Fund Reimbursement Fee at the time of purchase and at the
time of redemption, although certain exceptions apply. The following
table sets forth basic investment and fee information for each
class. <BR>
