<td align="left" width="90%" valign="top">
<center><font size=6>Transporter Associate&#174</font></center>
<br>
<center><img src="senhr.gif" height="5" width="536"></center>
<br>
<font size=4>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<B>Transpoter Associate&#174</B> for Microsoft Windows is designed with Transporters, Consultants and Brokers in mind. <I>TA</I> provides a multitude of straight forward methods
for not only automating your work, but <U>streamlining</U> your operations:
</font>
<br> 
<center><I><FONT SIZE=5>Software Features</FONT></I>
<br><br>
<TABLE BORDER="2" CELLSPACING="0" CELLPADDING="10">
<tr align="center">
<td align="left"><IMG SRC=bullet2.gif width="15" height="13"> Client/Generator Contact Management
