</tr>
<tr align="center">
<td align="left"><IMG SRC=bullet2.gif width="15" height="13"> Waste Disposal History
</td>
<td align="left"><IMG SRC=bullet2.gif width="15" height="13"><i> State Government Reporting (fees &amp; taxes)</i>
